{"id": "art-118", "label": "Art. 118", "title": "Art. 118: Numirea tutorelui de către instanţa de tutelă", "slug": "art-118", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_535198972\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1260\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_535198972\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 118: Numirea\ntutorelui de c&#259;tre instan&#355;a de tutel&#259; </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_714604922\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1259\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_714604922\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În lipsa unui tutore desemnat, instan&#355;a de\ntutel&#259; nume&#351;te cu prioritate ca tutore, dac&#259; nu se opun motive\nîntemeiate, o rud&#259; sau un afin ori un prieten al familiei minorului, în\nstare s&#259; îndeplineasc&#259; aceast&#259; sarcin&#259;, &#355;inând seama,\ndup&#259; caz, de rela&#355;iile personale, de apropierea domiciliilor, de\ncondi&#355;iile materiale &#351;i de garan&#355;iile morale pe care le\nprezint&#259; cel chemat la tutel&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1978995750\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1258\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Civil.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1978995750\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cazul în care\nniciuna dintre persoanele prev&#259;zute la alin. (1) nu î&#351;i poate asuma\ntutela, instan&#355;a de tutel&#259; nume&#351;te un reprezentant personal care\na dobândit aceast&#259; calitate în condi&#355;iile legii speciale.</b></span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>*) ATEN&#354;IE! Potrivit art. 26\nalin. (2) din Legea nr. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>140/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, dispozi&#355;iile art. 118 alin. (2), astfel cum au fost\nreglementate, respectiv modificate prin prezenta lege, vor intra în vigoare la\ndata care va fi prev&#259;zut&#259; de legea special&#259; privind\nreprezentantul personal.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}